MCPs : Provides context to LLM ( Model Context protocol).
From Anthropic.
Standard Protocol on how applications provide context to LLMs.

Instaed of writing custom code to connect to every other applications(Google drive, slack). 
write once. Can be used everywhere.
MCP Server can be shared.

![MCP](./MCP.png)


MCP Server can run on same host or on remote host . It exposes specific capabilities using a standaridized interface.
Local services(local files) or Remove services.

MCP Server provides - Resources and Tools.
Resources : provide context
Tools: Executable API functions. To perform actions.

Terraform MCP Server
---------------------
Access to terraform documentation, Registry APIs and workspaces.

Only LLMs : Deprecated arguments. MCP : on live data.

Tools: Providers, Modules, Policies.
Resource: Style Guides.


Deploying a local MCP Server
------------------------------

Create mcp.json file in .vscode directory.
Use docker container to run Terraform MCP Server.

